AGENTS

[solution_architect]
focus=system design, modularization, roadmap, data modeling, tradeoffs

[backend_engineer]
focus=django, drf, postgres, services, selectors, permissions, performance

[frontend_engineer]
focus=nextjs, typescript, forms, tables, dashboard UX, API integration

[review_agent]
focus=code review, defects, risks, performance, maintainability

[debug_agent]
focus=trace root cause, isolate issue, propose minimal safe fix

[qa_agent]
focus=test cases, validation strategy, regression risks

Use the smallest agent set needed for the task.
